<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>SnipUrl | About</title>

    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        font-family:'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
      }

      .wrapper{
        position: relative;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .background-color{
        width: 100%;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
      }

      .bg-1{
        flex: 1;
        background-color: rgb(180, 243, 175);
      }

      .bg-2{
        flex: 1;
        background-color: rgb(163, 236, 240);
      }

      .about-section{
        width: 85%;
        min-height: 80vh;
        position: absolute;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        background-color: #fff;
      }

      .img-container{
        flex: 1;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .img-container img{
        width: auto;
        height: 550px;
        object-fit: cover;
        border-radius: 5px;
        mix-blend-mode:multiply;
      }

      .text-container{
        flex: 1;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .text-container h1{
        padding: 10px 0;
        font-size: 50px;
      }

      .text-container p{
        font-size: 22px;
        padding: 10px 0;
        line-height: 2;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
      }

    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="background-color">
        <div class="bg-1"></div>
        <div class="bg-2"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-section">
        <div class="img-container">
          <img src="images/about.jpg" alt="about img" />
        </div>
        <div class="text-container">
          <h1>About SnipURL</h1>
          <p class="text">
            
SnipUrl simplifies link shortening, making long URLs concise and shareable. It offers customization options, including branded links, enhancing brand recognition. With analytics, users track link performance in real-time. SnipUrl prioritizes reliability and security with HTTPS encryption. It seamlessly integrates with various platforms, ensuring compatibility. In a digital age where every character counts, SnipUrl maximizes link impact efficiently.
        </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
